      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but even if it's meant to be neutral, isn't it a problem if the original meaning was written by a group of people who didn't even include women or certain minorities in their \"democratic\" process? doesn't that make the whole theory inherently biased toward a specific historical viewpoint rather than being truly objective?",
